==Sister cities==
Gastonia has two sister cities:
* Gotha, Thuringia, Germany 
* Santiago de Surco, Lima, Peru

Gotha was Gastonia&#x27;s first sister city in 1994. Santiago de Surco became an official partner in March 2004. Mayor Jennie Stultz visited Gotha in 2007. In December 2007, the mayor of Santiago de Surco visited for the annual lighting of the Christmas tree in the Rotary Pavilion. He was invited to light the tree along with one of the city&#x27;s councilmen.

