Other newspapers distributed throughout the city are:
*&quot;The Herald-Sun&quot;, from Durham
*&quot;The News &amp; Observer&quot;, from Raleigh
*&quot;The Oxford Ledger&quot;
*&quot;The Franklin Times&quot;

